{"tid":433308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康對英人權領袖被拒入境感不安 已聯絡駐港英領事館","createTime":"2017-10-12T09:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T09:47:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9618e50da3243329bda7054c5b8d5bc889247a2f","tid":433308,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T09:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171012/large/1507800021_9e84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171012%2Flarge%2F1507800021_9e84.jpg&h=a73c1f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾聲援被判囚的雙學三子的英國保守黨人權委員會副主席Benedict Rogers，被拒入境香港，Rogers指事前已接獲中國大使館預先告誡將被拒入境香港，意味有關決定來自中國政權，他為香港感到悲哀。前港督彭定康向英國《衛報》表示，事件令人不安，亦感到難以理解<br />\n<br />\n彭定康強調，Rogers持有效英國戶照，符合一切英國公民入境香港的條件，但竟被拒絕入境且沒有作出解釋。他已聯絡過英國外相約翰遜，也聯絡了駐港英領事館了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今早出席電台聯播節目時回應事件時，指特區的外交屬中央事務，要看入境問題，是否涉及外交，但她不便透露詳情。約翰遜已要求香港及中國解釋。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康早前曾指國家主席習近平的計劃應是讓大家認為爭取香港更多民主或高度自治的人是會被拘禁。他當時警告這已不單是英國責任，美國和歐洲都須關注香港，並有責任向爭取民主人士提供支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57323585&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57323585%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171012&d=nVwXi2MG8Clo8RYKanolAvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=dc793c58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57323585%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171012&h=9b25a4c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57323585&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171012</a>"},{"pid":"adf721a0c27e3755b204e4e4577c91cd5602f5e2","tid":433308,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"督爺, 請開條生路俾香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d2a9cbc8267470ee6d793ad41841795417541f","tid":433308,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T09:47:33.000Z","msg":"肥彭，今舖食粥食飯睇你喇<br />\n<br />\n快啲爭取bno居英權"}]}